             |            N |       Double | NNNNNNNNNNNN |
             |              |              | NNNNNNNNNNNN |
             |              |              |           NN |
             +--------------+--------------+--------------+
             |            1 |            2 |            1 |
             |            2 |            4 |            2 |
             |            3 |            6 |            3 |
             |            4 |            8 |            4 |
             |            5 |           10 |            5 |
             +--------------+--------------+--------------+).gsub(/^ +/m, "")
